## Phase Transitions

When the runner detects a phase boundary (all stages in a phase complete), it performs transition work:

- **Phase 1 → Phase 2**: No transition needed (same Rust crate)
- **Phase 2 → Phase 3**: `wasm-pack build` + copy `pkg/` to frontend directory
- **Phase 3 → Phase 4**: No transition needed (same frontend project)
- **Phase 4 → Phase 5**: No transition needed (same frontend project)

